title: Tracey Lynn Kirkpatrick // 52
description:
In March 1989, a 17 year old girl went to her job in Frederick, Maryland at a clothing store after school. Hours later, she would be found dead in the shop. After a few months passed, an anonymous man left a message for a confession hotline stated that he was the one behind the crime. Yet to this day, people believe that the investigation was purposefully botched to cover up a suspicious police officer.
